1. install rvm
2. switch to jruby
    $ rvm jruby
3. install bundler
    $ gem install bundler
4. let bundler bundle all gems
   (./.bundle/config puts them all under src/main/resources/ruby/vendor/gems/jruby)
    $ bundle install
5. also install jenkins-plugins.rb gem into src/main/resources/ruby/vendor/gems/jruby
    $ ./install-jenkins-plugins.rb
